workflow.name: SEO On-site Audit
workflow.description:
Automated SEO Audit in n8n ‚Äì Your All-in-One Website Optimization Tool!

Looking for a powerful, fully automated solution to analyze your website‚Äôs SEO? Our custom n8n workflow is designed just for you!

What does this workflow do?
Our advanced SEO audit collects all the essential data that impact your site‚Äôs search engine rankings, including:

Analysis of meta tags (title, description) with actionable optimization recommendations

Verification of H1 and H2 headings, presented in clear, organized tables

Checking internal, external, and broken links for full link health insights

Detection of key technical files: robots.txt and sitemap.xml

Identification of Google Analytics and social media links implementation

Evaluation of URL friendliness and mobile responsiveness

SSL certificate and noindex meta tag presence checks

Integration with Google PageSpeed API for website speed and performance metrics

DeepSeek API support for in-depth content and keyword analysis

Generation of clean, user-friendly HTML reports ready to share with clients or teams

Why choose this workflow?
Easy integration ‚Äì just connect your Google PageSpeed and DeepSeek API keys, and the workflow automatically gathers and analyzes all data.

Fully automated ‚Äì run the workflow and get a comprehensive SEO report with zero manual work.

Scalable ‚Äì audit single pages or entire website portfolios effortlessly.

Customizable ‚Äì pre-built functions and templates ready for extension or integration with your systems.

Professional HTML report ‚Äì visually appealing and packed with actionable insights for your team or clients.

How to get started?
Set up your Google PageSpeed and DeepSeek API keys.

Connect them within n8n ‚Äì no extra steps needed!

Run the workflow and receive a detailed SEO audit report that will help you improve rankings and boost traffic.

Automate your SEO audits with n8n ‚Äì faster, easier, and more effective than ever before!
